metadata.name: "Some Go, Some Stay, Some Come"
metadata.description:
This is a 100 piece edition to celebrate the New Year called "Some Go, Some Stay, Some Come".

Another year in the NFT space full of new projects, artists, collectors, drama, happiness and friendships is over and we are welcoming a new year where some of us leave, some of us stay and new ones come and join this crazy and adventurous ride.

Each token in this edition may to be redeemed for a free mint of my upcoming art series in Q2 2023 ðŸ¤«
